name: RE-03_W [Resolution of the Energy _white]
description: v4w.enko - "RE-03_W [Resolution of the Energy _white] " concept. Cells of abstract energy are populated in different layers. Cells of energy are applied to the cells of the digital body and lofted.  The whole body gets transformed in " Slow Motion" mode. Sound is generated from cells by  tracking system. Audio visual piece of generative abstraction has the dimension of 1024*1024 px matrix.
